    <abstract id="aspace_f578cc6f2c15cf9c86e72058c1ed2edc">This collection contain 21 memorial booklets from a variety of Byzantine and Roman Catholic Churches, 1949-1978. The booklets commemorate a variety of church events including dedications, rededications, anniversaries, building fund drives, and consecrations.</abstract>
